<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN""http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd"><HTML lang="ja"><html><head><title>Grammar Quiz</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><style type="text/css"><!--.style5 {color: #FF00FF}--></style></head><!-- created by Fred Bickerstaff --> <script LANGUAGE="javascript" type="text/JavaScript">		var numQuestions = 11;		var numAnswered = 0;		var numCorrect = 0;		var q_id=267; 			</script><SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript" SRC="../../../../js/quiz_top.js"></SCRIPT><LINK href="../../../../css/particleQuiz.css" type=text/css rel=stylesheet><body class="backgroundColor"><h2 class="titleText" align="center"> ぶんぽうクイズ </h2><div class="backgroundLayer" align="center" id="quiz"><div class="innerTitle">611D Yookoso II Chapter 2 〜をあげる／くれる／もらう (giving and receiving)</div><div class="quizlistLine"><a href="../../../../gquiz.php">Return    to Practice Quizzes list page</a></div>     <p align="left" height="100px" class="instructionLine">Complete the sentence(s) for each situation using : (a) a giving term and (b) a receiving term. Use the kanji used in the situation given.<br><br>   Before you start, study the examople below.<br>Example: <br>スミスさん --> キムさん <span class="style5">(Smith gave Kim someting; &quot; "〜さん”indicates that Smith and Kim are friends)</span>：　<br>本 <span class="style5">(This is what Smith gave Kim.)</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(a) スミスさんはキムさんに本をあげました。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b) キムさんはスミスさんに本をもらいました。</p>  <FORM name="quiz">	<! Question 1>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>1. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;町田さん -->  ジョーンズさん：　キャンディー <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;町田さんは	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('ジョーンズさんにキャンディーをあげました',this.value,0)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 2>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b)&nbsp;&nbsp;ジョーンズさんは	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('町田さんにキャンディーをもらいました',this.value,1)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 3>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>2. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;サイモンさん --> 私：　とけい<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;サイモンさんは	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('私にとけいをくれました',this.value,2)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>		<! Question 4>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b)&nbsp;&nbsp;私は	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('サイモンさんにとけいをもらいました',this.value,3)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>					<! Question 5>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>3. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;先生 --> 私たち：　日本のまんが<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;先生は		<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('私たちに日本のまんがをくださいました',this.value,4)" style="width: 350px;">	</SELECT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 6>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b)&nbsp;&nbsp;私たちは	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('先生に日本のまんがをいただきました',this.value,5)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 7>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>4. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;山田さん --> 私の子ども：　テレビ<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;山田さんは		<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('私の子どもにテレビをくれました',this.value,6)" style="width: 350px;">	</SELECT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 8>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b)&nbsp;&nbsp;私の子どもは	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('山田さんにテレビをもらいました',this.value,7)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 9>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>5.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;私 --> 先生：　花<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;私は		<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('先生に花をさしあげました',this.value,8)" style="width: 350px;">	</SELECT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>			<! Question 10>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>6.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;私 --> ロンさん：　いぬ<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;私は	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('ロンさんにいぬをあげました',this.value,9)" style="width: 350px;">    </INPUT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 11>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>7.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;私 -->  花：　水<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (a)&nbsp;&nbsp;私は		<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('花に水をやりました',this.value,10)" style="width: 350px;">	</SELECT>&nbsp;。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	</FORM><div id="score"></div><div><table class="optionBox"><tr>	<td><BUTTON onClick="checkAnswers()">Check Answers</BUTTON></td>	<td><BUTTON onClick="resetValues()">Reset Values</BUTTON></td></tr></table></div></div></body></html>